# ğŸ’° FinTrack - Simple Java Expense App

FinTrack is a small Java Spring Boot application for managing **departments** and **expenses**.  
It is a practice project to learn **Java**, **Spring Boot**, **REST APIs**, and **JWT authentication**.
 demo link : https://financretrackfront.netlify.app

